(von Roser, 1840)
</emphasis>
(Peloropeodinae)
</taxonomicName>
— 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[917,1107,1233,1259]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
new to 
<collectingCountry box="[1003,1107,1233,1259]" name="Portugal" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Portugal</collectingCountry>
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
